title: Map of the City of Los Angeles showing the confirmed Limits
name: Map of the City of Los Angeles showing the confirmed Limits
description:
the city map is taken from the 1849 survey and placed within a greater scope survey of the donation lots in 1857; the blocks matching current downtown los angeles are problematic because they display planning rather than actual buildings. 

Collection Source: UCLA Bruman Map Collection 
Call Number: G4364 LA NS HUP 1849-1857/1972 h.
